#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kronometer; is a stopwatch for &kde;. It can be used for basic tasks "
#| "like timer start/pause/resume, as well as lap times recording."
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is a stopwatch application. It can be used for basic tasks like "
"timer start/pause/resume, as well as lap times recording."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je štoperica za &kde;. Može se koristiti tza osnovne zadatke "
"kao što su start/pauza/nastavi, kao prolazna vremena snimanja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is able to save a complete session (timer and lap times) and to "
"restore it later."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je u stanju da sačuva cijelu sesiju (timer i prolazna vremena) "
"i da je vratite kasnije."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
