#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is a simple stopwatch application. It is meant to be simple and "
"pleasant to use, thanks to a use cases driven development."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je jednostavna aplikacija štoperica. To znači da je jednostavna "
"i ugodna za korištenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; main features are the following:"
msgstr "&kronometer; glavne karakteristike su sljedeće:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; provides a timer that can be started, paused, resumed and reset."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; pruža tajmer koji se može pokrenuti, zaustaviti, nastaviti i "
"resetovati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to record lap times and export them to a file."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; omogućava snimanje prolaznih vremena i snimanje u datoteku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to save a session and restore it later."
msgstr "&kronometer; vam omogućava da sačuvate sesiju i vratite kasnije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kronometer; allows you to copy timer numbers from display."
msgid "&kronometer; allows you to copy the timer numbers from its display."
msgstr "&kronometer; vam omogućava da kopirate brojeve timer sa ekrana."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Upotreba"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "General Usage"
msgstr "Opšta upotreba"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; main use case is of course the interaction with the timer. You "
"can start/pause/resume the timer by clicking on the proper actions in the "
"toolbar or in the &kronometer; menu."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; glavno korištenje je slučaj u interakciji sa vremenom. Možete "
"pokrenuti/pauzirati/nastaviti tajmer klikom na odgovarajuće radnje u alatnoj "
"traci ili u &kronometer; menija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Even simpler, you can use the keyboard instead of the mouse: you start the "
"timer with the keyboard's <keycap>Space</keycap> and you pause the timer "
"with <keycap>Space</keycap> too. You might recognize this behavior from many "
"media player applications."
msgstr ""
"Čak i jednostavnije možete koristiti tastaturu umjeto miša: počrećete tajmer "
"sa tipkom tastature <keycap>Space</keycap> i također pauzirate tajmer sa "
"tipkom tastature <keycap>Space</keycap>. Možete prepoznati ovo korištenje iz "
"mnogih media player aplikacija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "By pressing the <keycap>Enter</keycap> key when the timer is running, you "
#| "freeze that particular time and you create a new <emphasis>lap</emphasis> "
#| "time. These times are always visible in the table on the left of the "
#| "application, where you can sort them by clicking the <emphasis>Lap time</"
#| "emphasis> column's header. You can also add a custom text annotation to "
#| "each lap, by double-clicking the cells within the <emphasis>Note</"
#| "emphasis> column."
msgid ""
"By pressing the &Enter; key when the timer is running, you freeze that "
"particular time and you create a new <emphasis>lap</emphasis> time. These "
"times are always visible in the table on the left of the application, where "
"you can sort them by clicking the <emphasis>Lap time</emphasis> column's "
"header. You can also add a custom text annotation to each lap, by double-"
"clicking the cells within the <emphasis>Note</emphasis> column."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom na tipku <keycap>Enter</keycap> kada je timer pokrenut, vi "
"zaustavljate vrijeme i kreirate novi vremenski <emphasis>krug</emphasis>. "
"Ova vremena su uvijek vidljiva u tabli na lijevoj strani aplikacije, gdje "
"možete sortirati klikom na <emphasis>vrijeme kurga</emphasis> u kolona "
"zaglavlja. Tadođer možete dodati prilagođenu tekstualnu napomenu za svaki "
"krug, sa dvostrukim klikom na ćeliju unutar kolone sa <emphasis>napomenama</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The menubar (hidden by default) provides access to all commands and "
"configuration options. The menubar can be toggled with <guimenuitem>Show "
"Menubar</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></"
"keycombo>) from the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu or the menu button in "
"the toolbar."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Save and restore sessions"
msgid "Save and Restore Sessions"
msgstr "Sačuvajte i vratite sesiju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:107
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you pause a running stopwatch you create a session: a stopwatch time "
#| "and zero or more lap times. You can save a session on a file and you can "
#| "restore it later."
msgid ""
"When you pause a running stopwatch you create a session: a stopwatch time "
"and zero or more lap times. You can save a session and you can restore it "
"later."
msgstr ""
"Kada zustavite štopeticu vi kreirate novu sesiju: vrijeme stoperice je nula "
"za sve krugove. Možete sačuvati sesije u datoteku i kasnije ih možete "
"obnoviti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Save a session"
msgid "Save a Session"
msgstr "Snimi sesiju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Pause a running stopwatch, then click on the <guibutton>Save As</"
#| "guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. "
#| "Then choose a name for the session's file to be stored on your computer."
msgid ""
"Pause a running stopwatch, then click on the <guibutton>Save As</guibutton> "
"button in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. You can choose a name for the "
"session that you are going to save."
msgstr ""
"Zaustavljanje štoperice, a zatim klik na <guibutton>Snimi kao</guibutton> "
"dugme na alatnoj traci ili  u meniju <guimenu>File</guimenu>. Zatim "
"odaberite ime datoteke za sesiju i sačuvajte na svoj računar."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Restore a session"
msgid "Restore a Session"
msgstr "Obnovi sesiju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
#| "<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. Then choose an existing session's file to "
#| "be loaded."
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. Then choose an existing session to be loaded "
"from the session's dialog."
msgstr ""
"Klik na dugme <guibutton>Otvori</guibutton> na alatnoj traci ili u meniju "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. Zatim odaberite datoteku postojeće sesije da se "
"učita."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:127
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Update a session"
msgid "Update a Session"
msgstr "Ažuriranje sesije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the session is restored, you can resume the stopwatch and you can "
#| "record new lap times. If you want to save the updated session, you can "
#| "simply click the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button in the toolbar or in "
#| "the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu."
msgid ""
"When the session is restored, you can resume the stopwatch and you can "
"record new lap times. If you want to save the updated session, you can "
"simply click the <guibutton>Save</guibutton> button in the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Kada je sesija obnovljena, možete nastaviti štopericu i snimiti nova "
"prolazna vremena. Ukoliko želite da sačuvate ažuriranu sesiju, jednostavno "
"kliknite na dugme <guibutton>Save</guibutton> na alatnoj traci ili u meniju "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Update a session"
msgid "Edit a Session"
msgstr "Ažuriranje sesije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
#| "<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. Then choose an existing session's file to "
#| "be loaded."
msgid ""
"Click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button on the toolbar or in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. If you select an existing session in the "
"session's dialog, you will be able to:"
msgstr ""
"Klik na dugme <guibutton>Otvori</guibutton> na alatnoj traci ili u meniju "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. Zatim odaberite datoteku postojeće sesije da se "
"učita."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rename the session, by double-clicking on its name."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the session, by pressing <keycap>Del</keycap>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a note to the session or edit it."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Additional Features"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Export lap times"
msgid "Export Lap Times"
msgstr "Izvoz prolaznih vremena"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you record one or more lap times, the export features in the "
#| "<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu is made available, under the entry "
#| "<guimenuitem>Export laps as</guimenuitem>. Click on it and then choose a "
#| "name for the exported file. You can export in the Comma Separated Values "
#| "(CSV) format or in the &XML; one."
msgid ""
"When you record one or more lap times, the export features in the "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu is made available, under the entry "
"<guimenuitem>Export laps as</guimenuitem>. Click on it and then choose a "
"name for the exported file. You can export in the Comma Separated Values "
"(CSV) format or in the JSON one."
msgstr ""
"Kada snimate jedno ili više prolazno vrijeme, izvoz je moguć u meniju "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>, pod stavkom <guimenuitem>Izvoz prolaznih "
"vremena kao</guimenuitem>. Kliknite na tu stavku i zatim odaberite ime "
"datoteke. Možete snimiti kao datoteku u formatu sa odvojenim zarezima (CSV) "
"ili kao &XML; datoteku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:163
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Clipboard support"
msgid "Clipboard Support"
msgstr "Međuspremnik podrška"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is able to copy the current stopwatch time to the system "
"clipboard. Use the <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> key "
"combination or the <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> entry in the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je u mogućnosti da kopira trenutno vrijeme štoperice i spremi "
"ga u međuspremnik. Koristite <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> "
"kombinaciju tipku ili <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> stavku u meniju "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; is customizable in many aspects. You can open the settings "
"dialog clicking on the <guimenuitem>Configure &kronometer;</guimenuitem> "
"entry in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu. The settings dialog is "
"organized in the following categories."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; je prilagodiv u mnogim aspektima. Možete otvoriti klikom "
"dijalog postavki na <guimenuitem>Konfiguracija &kronometer;</guimenuitem> "
"stavku menija <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu>. Dijalog postavke su organizirane "
"u sljedećim kategorijama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "General settings"
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Opće postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the interface settings page you can choose whether to disable the laps "
#| "recording feature. This can be useful if you wish to optimize the window "
#| "content. You can also choose whether to show the time headers. The time "
#| "headers are the labels on the upper space of the stopwatch display. They "
#| "show the name of each timer component (hours, minutes, &etc;)."
msgid ""
"In the general settings page you can find the settings for the stopwatch and "
"for the laps. Under the stopwatch tab you can set your preferred time format "
"for the stopwatch display. You can choose whether to show hours, minutes or "
"second fractions (while seconds are always shown). &kronometer; supports "
"time granularity up to millisecond, although this requires high CPU usage "
"due to the high refresh rate of the User Interface."
msgstr ""
"U postavkama interfejsa možete odabrati da li ćete iskljuciti snimanje "
"prolaznih vremena. Ovo može biti korisno ukoliko želite opimizirati sardžaj "
"prozora. Također možete odabrati da li ćete pokazati vrijeme zaglavlja. "
"Vreme zaglavlja su oznake na gornjem dijelu ekrana štoperice. One prikazuju "
"vrijeme svakog timera komponente (sati, minute, &etc;)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Within the laps tab you can enable or disable the laps recording feature. If "
"the laps are enabled, you can choose their time format, whether to show "
"their notes and whether to show their absolute times, which are the "
"stopwatch times when they were recorded."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:195
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Font settings"
msgid "Font Settings"
msgstr "Postavke fonta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the font settings page you can customize the font of the stopwatch "
#| "display. You can choose different font families, styles and sizes for "
#| "each timer component (hours, minutes, &etc;)."
msgid ""
"In the font settings page you can customize the font of the stopwatch "
"display. You can choose different font families, styles and sizes for each "
"timer component (hours, minutes, &etc;). By default every timer component "
"will use the same font, according the current default font in the system."
msgstr ""
"U postavkama fonta možete prilagoditi font ekrana štoperice. Možete odabrati "
"različite fontove, stilove i veličinu za svaku komponentu timera (sati, "
"minute, &etc;)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Color settings"
msgid "Color Settings"
msgstr "Podešavanja boja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In the color settings page you can customize the default color of the "
#| "stopwatch display. You can change the background color and the text color."
msgid ""
"In the color settings page you can customize the default color of the "
"stopwatch display. You can change the background color and the text color. "
"The default colors will respect the currently selected system's theme."
msgstr ""
"U postavkama boje možete prilagoditi podrazumjevanu boju ekrana štoperice. "
"Možete promijeniti boju pozadine i boju teksta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:211
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kde; Built-in settings"
msgid "&kde; Built-in Settings"
msgstr "&kde; ugrađene postavke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kronometer; makes use of the standard &kde; configuration tools. You find "
"them in the <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> menu, under the "
"<guimenuitem>Configure shortcuts</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Configure "
"Toolbars</guimenuitem> entries. They allow you to change the shortcuts of "
"the &kronometer;'s actions, and to change the position of the toolbar and "
"its content."
msgstr ""
"&kronometer; koristi standardne &kde; postavke alata. Možete ih naci u "
"meniju <guimenu>Postavke</guimenu>, ispod stavki <guimenuitem>Postavke "
"prećica</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Postavke alatne trake</guimenuitem>. "
"One omogućuju da promijenite prećice &kronometer;, i promijenite položaj "
"alatne trake i njen sadržaj."

